The primary relief sought is injunctive relief, as stated in the Complaint (Epic Games to Apple_7e646bdc, Title Page) and confirmed by the Civil Cover Sheet (along with complaint)_7e7dea8d, which mentions "preliminary injunction" as a possible demand. Specific monetary amounts are not stated in the available documents.

