## Case Overview
This is a civil litigation initiated by Epic Games, Inc. against Apple Inc., filed as Case 4:20-cv-05640. The core of the dispute revolves around Apple's App Store policies and its alleged anti-competitive conduct in the iOS app distribution and in-app payment processing markets. Epic Games seeks injunctive relief to prohibit Apple's conduct and restore competition.

## Parties

| Role | Name | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| Plaintiff / Claimant | EPIC GAMES, INC. | A company that develops and publishes video games, including Fortnite. |
| Defendant / Respondent | APPLE INC. | A technology company that designs, manufactures, and markets mobile devices and operates the App Store. |

