## Case Overview
This legal matter involves a complaint for injunctive relief filed by Epic Games, Inc. against Apple Inc., alleging anti-competitive conduct related to Apple's control over the iOS App Store and its in-app purchase system. The case seeks to challenge Apple's policies and restore competition in the relevant markets. The current litigation stage is unknown, but based on the filing of a complaint, it is in the early stages.

